games.description: Can you fill this maze with a single touch? Light Line is a game where you fill in every empty square with a single touch. Try harder stages as much as possible. Move the light lines to the delight of filling in the blanks perfectly.
games.instructions: There are random shape of continuing blocks and one of them are colored. Start with touching the colored box, continually slide all the blocks to fill all the spaces. You should not take off the finger while sliding. If you are stuck with certain stage, you can check the free hints or paid hints with watching an ad.

games.description: Step into the glamorous world of Black Pink St. Patrick’s Day Concert, the ultimate dress-up game! Style your favorite Black Pink members with trendy outfits, accessories, and makeup to make them shine for their St. Patrick’s Day performance. With simple controls and endless creativity, this game is perfect for quick fun or long gaming sessions.
games.instructions: Left Mouse button Click or Tap to Play

games.description: Jump into action! ? Test your logic and reflexes in this addictive game. Collect slugs, upgrade your hero, and uncover the secrets of a mysterious planet! ?✨

Click on the left or right side of the screen to move diagonally on a cell. If you make a mistake, you can go back. Get as far as you can to find out all the secrets of this mysterious planet!

games.description: The famous merge game is arrived! You can shoot the planets like balls to throw, and when the same planets touch each other, it becomes bigger planet! Cute planets want to be bigger, so keep merge the planets until you make the sun!

At random timing, you can use extra help from strolling space ship, Space Tornado or 'Beyond space' button after you click them.

games.description: Noob Shooter: Gun Battle 3D is an exciting cooperative shooter created for true fans of action and intense battles. If you like games like CS, Warface and CoD, then this project will definitely not disappoint you. Join your team and engage in battle against opponents, striving for the main goal - to get as many kills as possible. The team that first reaches the required number of frags will be the winner.

Desktop controls: WASD - movement; Mouse - view; Left mouse button - attack; Right mouse button - aim; Space - jump; Shift - run; R - reload; C - crouch; H - grenade; 1,2,3 - weapon selection; Mobile device controls - touch/swipe.

games.description: Smash the floor! Are you under stress? Maybe Stack Fall can help you to release the stress. As your ball keep breaking the floors to get to the goal, every smashing will ease your stress. It's time to break some stacks!
games.instructions: Touch the screen to drop the bouncy ball will smash all the pillars in the way down. If the ball hit the black part of the floor, it's a game-over, so try to avoid it to break the floor. If you collect the gauges and become a fiver mode, nothing can stop the ball.

games.description: Step into the glamour of ‘Celebrity Spring Manicure Design’! Explore a world of trendy nail art, vibrant colors, and chic designs. Join celebrities in setting the trend for spring nails. Elevate your style with creative manicures, from floral elegance to modern motifs. Immerse yourself in the art of nail fashion and transform your fingertips into a canvas of spring-inspired beauty.
games.instructions: Left Mouse Button Click

games.description: Get ready for an addictive block puzzle challenge! Drag and drop colorful blocks to clear lines and rack up points. Think ahead, make big matches, and unleash powerful Super Blocks to crush multiple lines at once! Stuck? Use boosters to keep the game going. With three chances to clear the center, aim for the highest score and climb the global leaderboard. Easy to play, hard to master—can you become the ultimate puzzle champion? Let the block-dropping fun begin!

Use boosters when you're stuck to keep the game flowing. Charge your energy meter to unlock Super Blocks, which clear multiple lines at once. You have three chances to clear the center for extra points. Plan your moves carefully, compete globally for the highest score, and unlock exciting titles as you progress!

games.description: MYSTERIOUS FEATURES Play 100+ Mahjong exciting levels! Dive into Agatha Christie's stories Use boosters and collect tile sets PLAY MAHJONG Mahjong Crimes is a puzzle game where you match tiles to find clues and solve crimes. Use power-ups to beat tricky levels and win awards! SOLVE CRIMES Join detective Hercule Poirot on the Orient Express to solve crimes in this Mahjong game! Match tiles to investigate, defeat thugs, and untangle mysteries. Fun guaranteed!

games.description: Chop chop chop, throw the knife, but don't hit the ball~! It's like the mastery of circus performer. Which means, it's fun! Let's be the master of throwing knives and bounce the ball to the sky!
games.instructions: The ball is bouncing up as it drop to the handle of the knife. As you throw knife higher as much possible, the ball bounce up higher! Let's challenge to throw many knives as fast as possible to reach the top without stabbing the ball.

games.description: Geometry Vibes X-Ball is ready to give you a completely different gaming experience! After the first game of the series, interactive new levels, challenge section and completely new store are waiting for you in X-Ball mode. Start your new adventure now in Geometry Vibes X-Ball game where you will find yourself avoiding obstacles, traps and gears in each level!
games.instructions: Click to "MOUSE LEFT-CLICK" or "UP ARROW" and hold to fly up. Release the button to dive down. In 2,3,4 Player game modes, other players are controlled with "UP ARROW", "H" and "L".

games.description: Sprunki 3D Shooter delivers nonstop action as you face off against waves of Sprunkies! Your mission is simple: shoot to survive as long as you can. Run out of ammo? Search the battlefield for scattered rounds to keep the fight alive. Gear up and prepare to take on the Sprunkies—can you last the challenge?
games.instructions: Use WASD to move around and left mouse click to shoot!

games.description: Welcome to the mysterious world of Ancient Egypt! Find matching tiles, solve mahjong levels and collect artifacts to uncover secrets of Giza valley, Old city, Desert and Nile. Discover how the Great Pyramid of Giza was constructed, how Egyptians learned to read hieroglyphs, why only the pharaoh could own a cat in Ancient Egypt and many more. games.description: Classic Match 3 Bubble Shooter Game with jello balls, challenges, a nice bird and a fantastic heroine. Enjoy with lots of fun levels travelling around the world.

games.description: Ready to become the best pediatric doctor in the world? Learn to use medical instruments, give first aid to patients? Play our doctor without downloads, registration and absolutely free!
games.instructions: Use your mouse (to play on your computer), or your finger (to play on your phone) to click and control the ✂ instruments you have chosen to treat patients. Follow the on-screen prompts and you'll start to succeed very soon!

games.description: Save My Pet is a fun and addictive puzzle game where you must protect your adorable pet from a swarm of angry bees! With increasing difficulty, unique challenges, this game will test your problem-solving skills and quick thinking. Can you keep your pet safe from harm? Play Save My Pet now and find out!

When the jelly block collides with tiles of the same number, they merge into a larger number.
games.instructions: Mouse click or tap to play

Tiles Matching is a puzzle game combining the game mechanics of Mahjong and Three in a Row (Match-3). A logical educational game for children and adults. With each level, the difficulty increases - not everyone can complete the game the first time. Challenge your intelligence.

games.description: The Counterfeit Bank: Fake Money Tycoon Simulator Think Plague Inc, but with counterfeit cash! Your goal: dominate the economy one fake note at a time. Taxes are soaring, inflation’s out of control, and recession looms—perfect chaos for your evil plan. Print counterfeit money, outsmart enforcers, and flood the market with fake cash to disrupt the system. Can you survive the chaos and take over the economy before time runs out? Mwahahaha!
games.instructions: Use front companies to hide your counterfeiting activities. Some are more profitable, others harder to detect. Choose your districts wisely. Some offer big rewards but are heavily enforced. Others provide easier inroads but lower returns. They say, "He who controls the money supply, controls the nation." The stakes are high. The clock is ticking. Tick tock.

games.description: The gaming world is facing a serious tree crisis. Evil forces are running wild, and the trees are in great danger. As a player, your mission is to protect these precious trees. Even when you're offline, your character will keep fighting to safeguard the trees, constantly accumulating experience and resources. In the game, there's also a group of cute little sapling creatures imprisoned by the evil forces. You need to rescue them one by one through battles, explorations, and so on.
games.instructions: In the mysterious game world, Evil forces are raging everywhere. As a player, you bear the sacred mission of guarding trees.During the battle, the character will automatically attack the enemy, continuously accumulating experience points and various resources. There are multiple maps with different styles in the game, ranging from tranquil forests to mysterious valleys.

games.description: Urgently save: the evil spirits are coming! You are a Fighter, who is attacked by hordes of zombies and all sorts of evil spirits! Don't let them eat you alive!
games.instructions: The goal of the game is to destroy zombies in a variety of ways, constantly improve your weapons and complete as many levels as possible! Controls: Movement - W, S, A, D Menu - ESC Shot - LMB Additional shot - RMB Dash - Space Shop - Enter Throw a grenade - G Place a turret - E Call for support - Q Take additional weapons - Tab

games.description: Logic meets strategy! Operate 3 types of buses in 8 vibrant colors, each requiring careful planning. Enjoy a stunning 3D environment, as you clear the way for the selected bus and collect passengers. Master the art of optimal movement.
games.instructions: Players move different colored buses placed in a parking lot, each with its own size and movement direction. The goal of the game is to clear paths to free the selected bus and collect matching passengers in the most efficient way possible.

games.description: Match & connect tiles of same color & be the master of pair matching puzzle game. In this you have to find and match the same objects. There are different objects.
games.instructions: Match The things to complete the game. Click on same objects to match them.

games.description: Master chess piece movements in ChessField! Navigate a 2D grid using classic chess rules—rooks move straight, bishops diagonally, and more. But there’s a twist: moving up also makes your piece fall! Challenge Your Mind: Start with simple levels to learn the mechanics, then tackle increasingly tricky puzzles. Think strategically and solve creative challenges to advance!
games.instructions: Move your piece following chess rules—rooks move straight, bishops diagonally, etc. Remember: moving up also makes your piece fall down. Solve puzzles by reaching the goal while avoiding obstacles. Think strategically to complete increasingly difficult levels!

games.description: Build and manage your dream shopping mall! Expand by adding new shops, upgrade interiors, serve customers, and boost your reputation. Invest wisely, assign priority shoppers, and earn extra income with delivery vehicles. Complete missions to unlock rewards!
games.instructions: Use the left mouse button to interact with the in-game UI. Plus and minus keys = change the size of the camera.

games.description: Get ready to test your driving skills in Real Car Parking Simulator. In the parking simulation game, you will face various parking challenges. With realistic controls and detailed environments,you’ll feel like you're actually behind the wheel. From parallel parking to tight garage spaces, this game offers many parking challenges.
games.instructions: Mouse click or tap to play

games.description: In Gluttony, you control a giant hole with an endless appetite! Move around, swallow everything in sight, and grow bigger. But be careful—you're allergic to the little cute monsters! Avoid them at all costs while feasting on everything else.
games.instructions: 1. Move the hole to devour everything in sight. 2. Avoid the little cute monsters—they're dangerous!

games.description: An exciting game in which you have to interact with a variety of objects, manage cells and create delicious cakes based on original recipes. 31 unique cakes! 6 ingredients that can be combined! More than a 13 000 customers!
games.instructions: Drag a coin to buy a random ingredient. Drag an ingredient to the cake cell to start baking. Tap the oven to bake. Feed the cat by dragging food onto it—it'll eat, pay, and leave. To refund a coin, drag the ingredient to the plate. If an ingredient is in the cake box, double-click or use "clear cells" to refund. Giving the wrong cake may upset the customer.

games.description: Money ping pong is a casual idle game where you need to deftly install money blocks, use them to reduce the space for balls and earn money faster and more money! There are many different maps and dozens of functional blocks Relaxing gameplay
games.instructions: Place money blocks on the field to create your own pinball strategy for making money. Buy upgrades to complete the level.

games.description: In Bomby, your mission is simple but challenging—arrange the blocks provided to guide the adorable chicks back to their nest! Use logic, strategy, and creativity to solve each puzzle and ensure the chicks find their way home safely.
games.instructions: Pull the slingshot and shoot the bird into the nest

games.description: Pull the Pins is a strategic puzzle game where you must carefully pull pins in the correct order to rescue a young boy and make him reach his brother. Each decision matters, as a wrong move could lead to failure. Plan your actions wisely and use problem-solving skills to ensure a successful rescue.
games.instructions: Tap or mouse click to play!

games.description: Hidden Mushrooms is a game for nature lovers and those who enjoy walking in the woods. Beautiful views of nature in different forests, fields, swamps and other places. Birds singing and cute animals help you relax, and the search for hidden mushrooms captures your attention. You will spend time usefully, because the game perfectly trains your observation skills! Do you like hidden object searches? Then be sure to try to find hidden mushrooms!
games.instructions: Each level has a new forest with its own type of mushroom. Use your keen eye and attention to spot the hidden mushrooms. When you spot a mushroom, tap on it to collect it. Collect mushrooms and unlock new levels. The menu shows the number of mushrooms needed to unlock each level. The first forest is available right away. Watch the mushroom counter in the menu to track your progress.

games.description: Are you ready to use your logical mind to save love? In Pin Puzzle-Love Story, you face a series of interesting and challenging levels. Pull pins in the right order to solve puzzles and help couples reunite. Each level is a new Logic puzzle that can only be successfully completed by pulling the right latch!
games.instructions: Mouse click or tap to play

games.description: An Exciting Puzzle Game for the Whole Family! ? Play together and train your brain every day! ?? Enjoy thrilling puzzles suitable even for the youngest players. With new levels added daily, there's always a fresh challenge waiting for you! Have fun, improve your skills, and become a true puzzle master! ??
games.instructions: In this game, your goal is to assemble a bright picture by moving pieces across the board. Simply drag and drop the pieces into the correct spots until the image is complete. Be careful, as some pieces may look similar, but only one spot is right for each. Once all the pieces are in place, you’ll see the beautiful picture come together! Enjoy the process and sharpen your attention!

games.description: Get ready to tidy up the shelves in Shelf Sweep! Dive into a fun and addictive sorting puzzle game where your goal is to clean up messy shelves layer by layer. Only the outermost layer of items is visible—clear them by matching three identical items, and reveal the hidden treasures beneath!
games.instructions: Select a visible item from the outermost layer of the shelf. Match three identical items to remove them from the shelf. Use your skills to clean up all the shelves and solve challenging puzzles!

games.description: Use your ship to navigate and jump between different planets across the galaxy, but be careful not to drift off into the vastness of outer space!
games.instructions: Click or tap to jump between planets.

games.description: Play a timeless game of dominoes where strategy rules and every move matters. Unlock exclusive trophies and collectible wooden sets as you progress. Perfect for puzzle enthusiasts seeking endless fun and challenges.
games.instructions: Dominoes involves placing tiles to match numbers and score points. You can customize your game with 8 collectible domino sets and choose between Block and Draw modes for varied gameplay. Accelerate your progress by collecting sets and unlock exclusive bonuses through the Trophy Road.

games.description: Try your hand at being a tattoo artist. Give your customers beautiful and crazy tattoos! Сhoose different styles and use different colors! And the most important - enjoy the gameplay experience.
games.instructions: Use various gameplay mechanics to complete the level and get more difficult orders. Feel like a salon manager, draw and complete more and more complex drawings.

games.description: Welcome to Animal Merge, where you evolve adorable creatures by merging bubbles! Launch, connect, and combine animal bubbles to create advanced species. Watch as identical animals merge into exciting new forms! Keep merging to reach the ultimate evolution and complete your goal. Use special tools to boost progress. With each level, the challenge grows—can you master merging and collect all the final animals? Jump in and start merging now!
games.instructions: To play Animal Merge, tap an animal bubble to select it, drag backward to aim, and release to launch. When two identical bubbles collide, they merge into an upgraded version. Keep merging to evolve creatures until you reach the final one!

games.description: Embark on a delightful fruit match-3 adventure with Bunny's Farm: Zen Match Master. Join your cheerful companion, Bunny, as you traverse diverse landscapes—from lush meadows and snowy peaks to desert dunes and tropical beaches. Match juicy fruits like oranges and peaches to solve engaging puzzles, uncover enchanting stories, and unlock new chapters in this relaxing yet challenging journey.
games.instructions: - Gameplay Basics: Swap adjacent fruits to align three or more identical ones, clearing them from the board. - Objective: Achieve specific goals for each level, such as reaching a target score or collecting designated fruits. - Power-Ups: Create special fruit combinations to generate power-ups that can clear rows, columns, or entire sections. - Progression: Advance through levels to explore new environments and encounter increasingly complex puzzles.

games.description: Furry Kung-Fu & Babushka is a humorous fighting game with fun cartoon graphics, where controlling Cat or Babushka you need to inflict the enemy a series of hand-to-hand strikes, managing to dodge the sinister ball and sausage, which every second flies at you. Engage in epic hand-to-hand combat with park troublemakers. Earn achievements, get coins, unlock player skins! Will you be able to throw enemy sausage back at them? How long can you hold out? It's time to find out!
games.instructions: Controls on PC: arrow keys. Control on mobile: swipe and tap on the screen. Punch left: left arrow / tap on the screen to the left of the player. Punch right: right arrow / tap on the screen to the right of the player. Combo: multiple taps to the side you want to combo / multiple taps to the left or right of the player.

games.description: Challenge your geography skills in World Flags Trivia! Identify the nation for each flag from three choices across 194 questions. Perfect your skills as you progress through increasingly tricky questions. Can you score a perfect game and become a true flag expert? Play now and find out!
games.instructions: Use a mouse or touchpad to play this game.

games.description: Chill Girl Clicker is a soothing, laid-back clicker game that’s perfect for unwinding and finding your zen. Just like its predecessor, Chill Girl Clicker, this game offers a serene and calming experience, but with a delightful twist: a charming girl as the main character, bringing a fresh and enchanting vibe to your screen.
games.instructions: Click to play!

games.description: Get ready for Pop Party, a fast-paced 2D physics puzzle game with a wild twist! Your goal? Merge them to create bigger, better versions before your jar overflows! Progress through the game and collect unique themes, each transforming the look of your balls: Can you master the chaos, merge your way to victory, and unlock every theme?
games.instructions: Use mouse or touch to interact with in game interface

games.description: Unlock your potential and prove your skills. Outplay your opponents using powerful kicks and unique power-ups. Finally let them know who is the boss with the emotes system - become a football legend today!
games.instructions: Use the arrow buttons to move and jump across the field. Perform various kicks with the ball buttons. Score more goals in the given time and win the match. Climb divisions and unlock all rewards. Random match powerups and player emotes are available.

games.description: Conquer as much territory as possible and beat the competition. A smooth drawing experience! Use your paper block to steal the area from your online opponents in this game. Capture as much space as possible and try to get the highest score in the lobby. If you move outside your own color, your tail becomes exposed. You will be eliminated when someone manages to catch your tail. So you need to take risks to expand your colored area.
games.instructions: Use your mouse to move around and cover the map with your color, you can also use the arrow keys on your keyboard or the WASD keys Drag over the other players' white space and paint, then create a connection with your own color to claim that area. When you move outside your color, your tail is exposed to attack. This means that other players can run into you and eliminate you. You'll be constantly battling with other players, whether it's to reclaim your territory or take theirs.

games.description: Want to begin a fun and relaxing fishing adventure? In Fish Shooting - Fish Hunter, you’ll become a fishing master. Use your skills and quick reflexes to catch various fish while enjoying a laid-back casual experience!
games.instructions: Mouse click or tap to play

Join Princess Bella on a magical adventure, matching jewels and crowns to uncover hidden treasures. Create powerful boosters like Royal Bombs, hammers, and arrows to clear obstacles and win big. Stunning graphics and an enchanting soundtrack bring the kingdom to life. Get ready for a royal journey full of fun and surprises!
games.instructions: Connect three or more items of the same type to remove them from the board. Every level has a goal that you have to achieve to proceed further. Focus on the goal and plan your moves carefully so that you don’t run out of them before completing the task! Use the Royal Bombs and Hammers to remove blockers and complete daily challenges for even more rewards.

games.description: Experience the thrill of jailbreak escape, find a way out to freedom in our adventure filled jailbreak games! In this exciting jailbreak escape journey, you’ll take on the role of a character trapped behind jail bars, where every level presents unique challenges and exciting mini games, leading to the final goal of prison escape. Your goal in this prison games? Outsmart the system, solve clever puzzles, and find a way out in this immersive jailbreak escape adventure.

games.description: Lambo Traffic Racing, you will be playing lambo cars through endless highway. It is a great game for kids and adults. Great fun, great graphics and great lambos to drive .

games.description: Take control in Airport Controller Game! Manage planes, guide safe landings, refuel, repair, and board passengers while handling growing airport traffic. Test your skills in this fast-paced simulation and keep everything running smoothly. Play now!

games.description: In a lost kingdom, disaster has struck! During a knight’s tournament, a mysterious figure in a black cloak suddenly appears. The stranger casts a spell on the king, causing him to vanish without a trace right before everyone’s eyes! The princess manages to escape from the castle, but where should she go now? How can she save her father and the entire kingdom? Will she be able to overcome all the challenges, find her father, and defeat the evil wizard?
games.instructions: The controls are quite simple: click on objects highlighted in green, gather resources, clear obstacles with them, and accomplish your objectives. Develop your strategy at the start of each level and achieve your goal! Every second counts!

games.description: Falling Blocks Puzzle is a timeless puzzle game where players arrange falling geometric shapes, to form complete horizontal lines. As lines are completed, they disappear, and players earn points. The game ends when the stack of shapes reaches the top of the screen. It’s a test of strategy and quick thinking, beloved by gamers worldwide.
games.instructions: Keyboard: ⚈ Left arrow: Move left ⚈ Right arrow: Move right ⚈ Dow arrow: Move down ⚈ Up arrow or X: Rotate right ⚈ Z: Rotate left ⚈ Space : Drop ⚈ Left arrow: Move left Mouse or touch: ⚈ Left mouse click (or touch): Rotate ⚈ Left mouse drag (or touch drag): Move ⚈ Drop button: Drop

games.description: Combine monsters and increase your power by thinking every action. You have to meet monsters, complete more than 100 tasks and learn the secret of the magician.
games.instructions: The goal of the game is to unravel the main mystery of the magician by completing more than 100 tasks, fighting and uniting various monsters. Players will have to gradually increase their magical power, thinking about every action and effectively managing resources.

games.description: Looking for an engaging casual shooter that’s easy to get the hang of but offers engrossing action and real tactical challenges? Agent Squad is a top-down shooting game with intelligent mechanics, loads of cool upgradable guns, and addictive gameplay
games.instructions: The gameplay is very simple, slide the screen or use keyboard to move and defeat all the enemies to successfully enter the next level. More cool guns are waiting for you to unlock! Join now, press the trigger wildly and feel the fun of shooting the game you! Have fun!

games.description: Dive into the exciting world of Dynamons Connect! This fun and engaging game with adorable, colorful characters helps improve focus and visual perception. Match identical tiles by connecting them with a path that has no more than two turns to clear the board. With endless levels, the challenge never stops!
games.instructions: ✔ Find two matching tiles and connect them with a path that has no more than two 90-degree angles. ✔ Clear the board before time runs out! ✔ Choose between two difficulty modes for the best experience. ✔ Keep playing as long as you want—unlimited levels mean unlimited fun!

games.description: Bus Driver Simulator 3D is a bus simulator in which you will be able to drive different types of buses traveling around different parts of the world including Los Angeles, Berlin, Rome, Alaska and so on. Each scenario in Bus Driver Simulator 3D has special characteristics. So, for example, in Alaska you will be driving on snowy tundra, and other cars will not be very much, but on the city highway in Los Angeles the traffic will be more intense.
games.instructions: Management: On mobile devices: Use the buttons on the phone screen. On PCs: - W-A-S-D keys to control the bus; - Spacebar - handbrake; - C - change camera view; - G - horn; - Q - left turn signal; - E - right turn signal; - Esc - pause.

games.description: Farm Block is an engaging farm-themed puzzle game where players slide adorable animal blocks to free them from the farm. Test your strategic thinking and enjoy the charming countryside setting! With its mix of puzzle-solving and elimination mechanics, Farm Block offers a fun and rewarding challenge for all ages.
games.instructions: 1️⃣ Slide animal blocks in the right direction to create space. 2️⃣ Match & Eliminate blocks strategically to clear the path. 3️⃣ Solve Puzzles with increasing difficulty levels. 4️⃣ Escape the Farm! Complete levels and rescue all the animals.

games.description: Color Nuts & Bolts Puzzle is a fun and engaging puzzle game that challenges your spatial imagination and color-matching skills! Match colorful screws to their corresponding nuts and watch as your puzzle-solving skills bring vibrant images to life. Perfect for players of all ages, this game offers hours of brain-teasing fun with a visually satisfying reward at the end of each challenge. Test your logic, precision, and creativity in this unique puzzle-solving adventure!
games.instructions: Objective: Match the colored screws to their corresponding nuts on the board.
